==Media==
in Angeles City, the only Cable TV channel is PEP TV on a cable provider Air Cable Channel 3 SD &amp; 209 in HD. There are three radio stations in the city: UFM 105.5, GVAM 792 and GV 99.1.

==Transport==
Clark International Airport is near the city; it is served by many passenger and cargo airlines, including some international ones.

